title: Yorick/Singed skins?
body: @rioters! I was just curious what happened to Arclight Yorick and Beekeeper Singed skins in patch 7.19?

replies.body: New skins don't necessarily release same day as the patch.  Keep an eye on our [News](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) page for more info to come!
